<slide fontsize="6em">
	<title>Building New Characters</title>

	<blurb>You can compose new characters from base characters with combining modifiers that use no "space".</blurb>
<break/>
	<blurb>Equivalents:</blurb>
	<example><![CDATA[     å != å 
U+0041 != U+00C5 + U+030A]]></example>

<break lines="3"/>
	<blurb>Alternative Order:</blurb>
	<example><![CDATA[a +  ̂ +  ̣ = ậ]]></example>
<break/>
	<example><![CDATA[a +  ̣ +  ̂ = ậ]]></example>
